# Output dumps from collect-live-state.sh.
#
# These contain raw cluster state including ConfigMaps, Argo CD Application
# specs, ingress rules, network policies, and per-host facts. They MUST
# stay out of git -- ConfigMap content in particular can carry plaintext
# config that the rest of this repo treats as sensitive.
#
# Secret values themselves are not exported (the script captures secret
# NAME + TYPE only), but the dump is still operator-only material.
output/
